<p>On click, the leaflet map displays the park boundary and zooms in to the boundaryâ€™s extent. This action also interacts with the slick carousel containing the photos from the parks, filtering to display only photos from the selected park. The slick carousel is set to autoplay through the photos. Thumbnails can be clicked to view a higher resolution version of the photos using the magnific-popup library. Iâ€™ve linked the magnific-popup controls with the slick carousel controls so that the slick carousel is always centered on the viewed photo.</p>

